        <item>
        <title>说说</title>
        <link>//localhost:1313/%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>//localhost:1313/%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4/</guid>
        <description>&lt;div class=&#34;daily-speak&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;speak-header&#34;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&#34;speak-date&#34;&gt;
            &lt;span class=&#34;date-day&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&#34;date-month&#34;&gt;5月&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&#34;date-year&#34;&gt;2025&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&#34;weather-tag&#34;&gt;☀️ 晴&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;speak-content&#34;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;重新测试了十六种人格测试，发生变化了，由原来的ISTP变成了INFP，果然人是会变化的。&lt;a target=&#34;_blank&#34; href=&#34;https://www.16personalities.com/ch/%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%BC%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95&#34;&gt;免费人格测试&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;daily-speak&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;speak-header&#34;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&#34;speak-date&#34;&gt;
            &lt;span class=&#34;date-day&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&#34;date-month&#34;&gt;5月&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&#34;date-year&#34;&gt;2025&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&#34;weather-tag&#34;&gt;☀️ 晴 &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;speak-content&#34;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;今天加入了碎碎念的功能，让ai帮忙设计了信息框的样式，我感觉还不错哦&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
    .daily-speak {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    position: relative;
}

.speak-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
}

.speak-date {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: system-ui;
}

.date-day {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2c3e50;
}

.date-month {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #6c757d;
    position: relative;
    top: -2px;
}

.date-year {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #95a5a6;
    font-weight: 300;
}

.weather-tag {
    background: rgba(255,193,7,0.15);
    color: #e67e22;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.speak-content {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #34495e;
}

/* 响应式调整 */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .speak-date {
        gap: 0.3rem;
    }
    .date-day {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .date-month {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .weather-tag {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
}
/* 基础标签样式 */
[class$=&#34;-tag&#34;] {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0 5px 5px 0;
    backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
}

/* 情感类样式 */
.mood-happy { background: rgba(255,193,7,0.15); color: #e67e22; }
.mood-sad { background: rgba(66,153,225,0.15); color: #4299e1; }

/* 环境信息类 */
.location-tag { background: rgba(46,204,113,0.15); color: #2ecc71; }
.environment-tag { background: rgba(52,152,219,0.15); color: #3498db; }

/* 技术信息类 */
.device-tag { background: rgba(155,89,182,0.15); color: #9b59b6; }
.platform-tag { background: rgba(231,76,60,0.15); color: #e74c3c; }

/* 动态数据类 */
.stats-tag { background: rgba(241,196,15,0.15); color: #f1c40f; }
.time-tag { background: rgba(52,73,94,0.15); color: #34495e; }
/* 基础链接样式 */
.speak-content a {
    color: #2b6cb0;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(43, 108, 176, 0.2);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* 悬停状态 */
.speak-content a:hover {
    color: #2c5282;
    border-bottom-color: currentColor;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}

/* 焦点状态 */
.speak-content a:focus {
    outline: 3px solid rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.5);
    outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* 访问过的链接 */
.speak-content a:visited {
    color: #553c9a;
    border-bottom-color: rgba(85, 60, 154, 0.2);
}

/* 活动状态 */
.speak-content a:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
    opacity: 0.8;
}

&lt;/style&gt;</description>
